page.title: 11Home Life Gipsey Bridge
page.content: According to a questionaire carried out in the village of Gipsey Bridge most of the people in our area keep some sort of pet.Usully these pets are acquired when very young and are the most popular.According to the record most people shampoo their pets.And some keep themsevles clean.One pet died young and one died after more than 10 years Five people had their pet since they were born.The food was tinned and dry food.Only one said they exercised their pet once the rest said never.Only one thought rats would make good pets the rest said they would not make good pets.
